CM_ BO_ 1000 "VEHICLE CONFIG BITMAP #1 Also see: Read by ID $0122 on the BCM?  Wrangler 1: $5531A253B40E51B8 Wrangler 1: $5531A25B4C0E51B8 Wrangler 2: $5131A243500E505C Wrangler 3: $493122530000511C  Capability bits? Usually static, difference seen between vehicles in first, fourth through eighth bytes.";
